def_cn: （组织中的成员）忠实的，积极的，得到承认的
def_en: If a person or country is a paid-up member of a group, they are an enthusiastic member or are recognized by most people as being a member of it.

def_cn: （政党或组织成员）已缴清会费的，正式的
def_en: If someone is a paid-up member of a political party or other organization, they have paid the money needed to become an official member.
